const content = "<div class=\"container single-page-container\">\n\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"nv-single-page-wrap col\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"nv-page-title-wrap nv-big-title\" >\n\t<div class=\"nv-page-title \">\n\t\t<small class=\"neve-breadcrumbs-wrapper\"></small>\t\t<h1>Insurance Statement</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n</div> \n\t<div class=\"nv-content-wrap entry-content\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">WorkSmart-AI Insurance Statement</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>WorkSmart-AI maintains appropriate insurance cover to ensure we operate responsibly and provide assurance to our clients and partners.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Insurance Cover</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We currently hold the following insurance policies:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Public Liability Insurance</strong> – £5 million cover</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Professional Indemnity Insurance</strong> – £1 million cover</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These policies provide protection for our clients, partners, and staff in the unlikely event of an incident or claim.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Purpose of Cover</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Public Liability</strong> – protects against claims for accidental injury or property damage during our training or consultancy activities.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Professional Indemnity</strong> – protects against claims arising from advice, consultancy, or training content.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Employers’ Liability</strong> – protects employees and contractors, as required by UK law (if applicable).</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Evidence of Insurance</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Copies of insurance certificates are available on request for procurement and compliance purposes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>📩 <a href=\"/contact-us/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://worksmart-ai.co.uk/contact-us/\">Contact us here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Review</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our insurance arrangements are reviewed annually to ensure appropriate levels of cover and compliance with industry best practice.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div>\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n</div>";
